        What You'll Do
        You will be at the core of bridging client business challenges with the capabilities of our Solutions.
        You will work closely with client representatives and McKinsey consultants in joint problem-solving sessions. Additionally, you will be responsible for driving the process of converting and enriching raw client data sources into the high added value datamart required for Solutions to deliver the insights related to the business challenges at stake.
        You will be expected to master the analytics and methodology embedded into the Solutions and the data concepts related to the Solution's functional or sector domains. You will accompany clients in their use of the Solutions to drive sustainable and high impact. This involves engaging with client sponsors on a regular basis to discuss about how to drive user adoption (leveraging our usage analytics framework), help them with questions they might have regarding the Solution usage or applicability, and more.